added.title: Sliding/Spinning Webs
added.description: Lucas and Findley find an ice cube. When Lucas rides the ice cube in the sink and falls down the drain, a scared Findley rallies to save him./ Lucas questions his spider-hood when he can't spin a web properly.

added.title: More Cowbell
added.description: Thomas is elated when he finds a cowbell on the side of the tracks, until his friends start hogging it.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Sir Topham Hatt's Hat
added.description: When Sir Topham Hatt's Hat blows away in the wind before making an important announcement, Thomas and his friends race around Sodor, trying to catch it. The Hat remains out of reach until they learn to work together.
added.originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

added.title: Too Hot to Handle/The Big Squeak/Big Jumping Spider
added.description: Findley can't resist some freshly baked cookies that are too hot to eat./ Avocado's new toy is driving everyone crazy with its noisy squeaker./ Lucas performs epic jumps all around House./ Findley is nervous and wishes Lucas wouldn't jump.

added.title: Ghost Camp/Boo/Never Boop a Robot
added.description: When Lucas and friends go camping, Avocado tells a scary story. Lucas now thinks there's a ghost in the garden./ Lucas loves to give his friends a scare on Halloween./ When Lucas boops a robot, he and his friends are chased around House!

added.title: Lonesome Lucas/I Can't See You/Don't Eat Me
added.description: Lucas wakes up in the middle of the night. How long can a night alone last?/ Lucas tries to beat Bodhi at Hide and Seek./ When Findley watches a show about spiders eating flies, he thinks Lucas wants to eat him!

added.title: I'm Taking You In/Something Up There/Home Sweet Home
added.description: When Arlo's mom is out, Lucas looks after him. How hard can it be?/ After hearing a screech from the fireplace, Lucas journeys up to find what is causing the noise./ Lucas and friends find a Gingerbread House and can't resist eating it.

added.title: Bye Bye Bee/Jeepers Peepers/House is Breathing
added.description: Saying goodbye can be hard, but there are ways to feel close to your friends./ Can Dimples finally beat Weebscuit at a staring competition?/ Lucas is convinced House is alive when the heating vent comes on.

added.title: Boingo/Findley's Bad Day/You Rang
added.description: Lucas, Findley and Bodhi become obsessed with a new toy called Boingo./ Findley is convinced House is out to get him./ Arlo is missing his mother, so Lucas gives him a bell to ring if he needs Lucas's help - bad idea.

added.title: Flash and Boom/ House Sitting/ Findley is Sick
added.description: Lucas and Findley are unnerved by the thunder and lightning. But Arlo helps them through it! / Findley is nervous about taking care of House while Lucas is away. / Findley fibs about being sick to avoid chores. Dr. Lucas isn't happy.

added.title: A Song for Wimble/ I Want My Baby Acorn Back/ The Giggles
added.description: Findley becomes nervous when he's put in charge of taking care of House while Lucas is away./ Lucas and Findley are a little unnerved by the thunder and lightning happening outside their window. But Arlo is there to help them through it!/ Dr. Lucas is in the house when Findley says he has a cold. But is Findley being truthful?

added.title: Woof
added.description: Bing and Flop are in the park, when a doggie called Sunshine comes to play catch with them! Bing loves playing with Sunshine, but what will happen when Bing realises he can't keep Sunshine?

added.title: Eggy Head
added.description: Bing and his friends are at Amma's creche today making Eggy Heads! Amma explains that Eggy Heads need 7 sleeps, water, light and patience to grow it's cress hair. But Bing has an idea to help his Eggy grow cress hair quicker...

added.title: Hack Attack
added.description: Nina doesn't like football, so she goes off to find a different game. Meanwhile, Roberto stands in as goalkeeper but after he gets hit with the ball one too many times, his circuits break down and he goes crazy. Quick! Someone fix Roberto!

added.title: Nina
added.description: Weird things are happening to Pato: his hose won't work and his favorite hat seems to have a mind of its own. Pato investigates and finds Nina, a tiny girl dressed in green who lives among the plants with her robot Roberto. Pato, you've made a new friend!

added.title: House of Colors
added.description: Elly has a new house and wants to paint it pink. She asks Pocoyo and Pato for help, but they want to paint it a different color. Teamwork involves compromise! They'll find a way to paint it a color they all like, that's for sure.

added.title: Disco Fleaver
added.description: Loula has fleas, so Nina uses her shrink ray to try to get them to leave Loula alone. But it turns out the fleas are in the middle of a massive party. Will our friends get Loula to stop scratching?

added.title: Bumbleberry Surprise
added.description: It's time for tea and our friends head out into the forest to pick berries. The key ingredient to make a delicious cake. But Pato eats the wrong berry... Nina, help poor Pato!

added.title: Great Shot!
added.description: Pocoyo and Nina are playing tennis until Pato switches the tennis ball for a basketball ball. Elly joins in and adds rugby rules. A straightforward tennis match has turned into a nonsensical combination of sports!
